                "comment": "Appreciate the input! Scannability was the #1 priority all shapes are tested and work. The bottom section of all the shapes is kept standard specifically for scanner reliability. While it’s perfect for boutique products, high-speed industrial production isn't off the table either, provided the barcode is sized correctly and pre-tested for the specific packaging. It’s all about finding that balance between art and function.",
